Sub download
============

Download italian subtitle for your favorite show. Example:

    $ subdl ~/Downloads/The.Simpsons.S24E14.HDTV.x264-LOL.mp4

Installation:

    $ gem install subdl

The application needs to access to your Itasa account. You need to save your 
credentials in the `~/.itasa-credentials` file using the following format:

    $ cat ~/.itasa-credentials
    username
    password


